<li><a href="#Follow-A-Fitness-Challenge">Follow A Fitness Challenge.</a></li>



<li><a href="#Practice-Active-Rest-Days">Practice Active Rest Days.</a></li>



<li><a href="#Set-Up-A-Home-Gym">Set Up A Home Gym.</a></li>



<li><a href="#Increase-Your-Protein-Intake">Increase Your Protein Intake.</a></li>



<li><a href="#Cut-Back-On-Processed-Food">Cut Back On Processed Food.</a></li>



<li><a href="#Drink-More-Water">Drink More Water.</a></li>
</ul>
